10. **Graviton Coupling and the Fine-Tuning of Inflation**: Examine the role of the collective graviton coupling $\alpha \sim 1/N$ in mitigating the fine-tuning problem of the inflationary vacuum energy. Assess whether the memory burden feedback mechanism provides a natural explanation for the smallness of $H$ relative to $M_{Pl}$ without requiring a bare cosmological constant.
\end{IDEAS}


